arStrings.szText: Have your taunts turned sour, Beleth? I can see you recognize my father's blade!
The tide has turned in your favor, and you are relishing the look of fear on your opponent's face. Projected as you call out to your opponent across a room. Pronounciation: Bell-Eth
N-no! Keep that accursed thing away!
Fear and cowardice as you realize you are no longer invulnerable.
